                              </para>
                            </label-para>
                          </para>
                        </label-para>
                        <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                          <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">ii</label>
                          <para>
                            <text>can be surrendered, retired, cancelled, or otherwise used to—</text>
                            <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                              <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">A</label>
                              <para>
                                <text>offset greenhouse gas emissions under<insertwords amend.level1="insert-unanimous">, or otherwise comply with,</insertwords> any enactment (whether of New Zealand<struckoutwords amend.level1="struckout-unanimous"> or of</struckoutwords><insertwords amend.level1="insert-unanimous">,</insertwords> another country<insertwords amend.level1="insert-unanimous">, or any jurisdiction of any country</insertwords>), rule of law, <struckoutwords amend.level1="struckout-unanimous">or </struckoutwords>contractual provision<insertwords amend.level1="insert-unanimous">, or international treaty or protocol</insertwords>; or</text>
                              </para>
                            </label-para>
                            <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                              <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">B</label>
                              <para>
                                <text>enable a person who surrenders, retires, cancels, or otherwise uses it to claim an environmental benefit</text>
                              </para>
                            </label-para>
                          </para>
                        </label-para>
                      </para>
                    </label-para>
                  </para>
                </def-para>
                <def-para id="DLM1474196" quote="1">
                  <para quote="1">
                    <text><def-term id="DLM1474197">greenhouse gas</def-term> has the meaning set out in section 31 of the Climate Change Response Act 2002</text>
                  </para>
                </def-para>
              </amend>
              <follow-text space-before="no">.</follow-text>
            </para>
          </subprov>
        </prov.body>
      </prov>
    </part>
